{"tid":251210,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"天之道，損有餘而補不足","createTime":"2017-05-20T17:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T07:32:12.000Z","uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81f607902b47920468477c3a1f5000b40324f776","tid":251210,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"是故虛勝實，不足勝有餘。其意博，其理奧，其趣深。天地之像分，陰陽之侯烈，變化之由表，死生之兆章。<br />\n<br />\n弱之勝強，柔之勝剛，天下莫不知，莫能行<br />\n天下之至柔，馳騁天下之至堅<br />\n<br />\n五指發勁，無堅不破，摧敵首腦，如穿腐土<br />\n人徒知枯坐息思為進德之功，殊不知上達之士，圓通定慧，體用雙修，即靜而動，雖攖而寧。<br />\n<br />\n鉛汞謹藏，就是說當固腎水，息心火，修息靜功方得有成。<br />\n<br />\n係咪金庸作出黎，係既話真係癲"},{"pid":"317fc9d0b4b299bbe80939760c38decd655e3506","tid":251210,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"請看 老子 道德經 七十七章"},{"pid":"ea009c06f0b81ccc1d74d9b1632ad25b3d84c428","tid":251210,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T20:18:11.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"9f2c49f8c7916280e4c06b92d0f3885af6f8f764","tid":251210,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T20:25:58.000Z","msg":"其實你呢段野都應該係google搵出嚟<br />\n點解你會唔知係道德經？<br />\nsearch result 冇㗎咩？"},{"pid":"2d467a211a2a99033a8cc448b8d0386984ad2c27","tid":251210,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你呢段野都應該係google搵出嚟<br />\n點解你會唔知係道德經？<br />\nsearch result 冇㗎咩？</blockquote><br />\n希望唔係有人手打"},{"pid":"b1f8f80542a4d3faea8e9a98a16f219e407fd43d","tid":251210,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"人之道，損不足而補有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eed9b363b4f9fbb5fcf345fd83cf2352d05ba74","tid":251210,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"370dd433b60be48a4b4787a477d30b66d89a53a1",